products.title: Choices Harrow Navy Roller Blind
products.metadescription:
With the faintest of lines coming through from the back, the choices harrow navy roller blind adds drama to a space in the gentlest of ways. And never has navy looked so good.  
In a darkened room, full of pattern and energy, this blind brings a theme altogether and addresses it
